sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Operator as Operator
    participant Script as start.sh / main_start.sh
    participant Compose as Docker Compose
    participant Backend as sre-agent-api
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Cache as Redis
    participant Dashboard as Next.js Dashboard

    Operator->>Script: Start the platform stack
    Script->>Compose: Load env and launch services
    Compose->>DB: Start database service
    Compose->>Cache: Start cache service
    Compose->>Backend: Start API and run migrations/seed
    Backend->>DB: Initialize schema and seed data
    Compose->>Dashboard: Start UI container
    Dashboard-->>Operator: Ready on the published port
